{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b73cecf3f","title":"只要多打几个胜仗整个国际局势就会改观","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"aaaa7db5a1","index":0,"year":1950,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"2b73cecf3f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"d38323d203","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭，指彭德怀，当时任中国人民志愿军司令员兼政治委员。邓、朴，指邓华、朴一禹，当时均任中国人民志愿军副司令员兼副政治委员。"},{"id":"812b5380f6","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"高，指高岗，当时任东北军区司令员兼政治委员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"be08344ab8","type":"title","text":"只要多打几个胜位整个国际局势就会改观","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f"},{"id":"d38323d203","type":"paragraph","text":"彭、邓、朴，并告高","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f"},{"id":"812b5380f6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）你们释放一批仔房很对，应赶快放走，尔后应随时分批放走，不要请示；（二）故方对我实力还认为是六万至七万人，“并不是一个不可悔的势力”，这点对我有利；（三）美、英、法对我毫无办法，悲观情绪笼罩各国，只要我军多打几个胜位，歼灭几万敌军，整个国际局势就会改观","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f"},{"id":"5f55757a00","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f"},{"id":"d7ac0c80d0","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f"}],"page":{"id":"21aa686bc8","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"2b73cecf3f","start":377,"end":377}}}},"__N_SSG":true}